data.description: 2.25% VA Assumable Loan!!! Welcome to this sprawling 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom home that offers the convenience of single-story living with the added bonus of two bedrooms and 1 full bath on the upper level. Located in a prime location near San Diego State University, this property is not only a great multigenerational home but also a fantastic rental opportunity. The main level offers a spacious living room with captivating views that will take your breath away, and a cozy brick fireplace.Hone your cooking skills in the well-appointed and updated kitchen with dark wood cabinets, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and dining area. Heading downstairs are 2 large bedrooms including the private and luxurious primary suite with beautiful fireplace, walk-in closet with closet system, and a spa-like bathroom with double sinks, enormous walk-in shower, and Jacuzzi tub. Whether you're seeking a tranquil space to unwind or a peaceful place to start your day, this primary suite delivers. The second downstairs bedroom has a walk-in closet with closet system and shares the full hall bath. Additional home features include all laminate hardwood flooring, and new flooring upstairs. Enjoy and entertain in the expansive backyard boasting a spacious patio perfect for dining al fresco. The huge lot offers potential for landscaping, a garden, and space for various activities. Within close proximity to shopping, dining, entertainment, transportation, and so much more. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your new home or investment property!
